about.description:

from small one-off projects to complete application suites.
about.summary: Version 3 of the Gtk+ graphical toolkit

    - xvfb-run -a -s "-screen 0 1024x768x24" bash -c 'gtk3-demo --run application_demo
      --autoquit'
    - xvfb-run -a -s "-screen 0 1024x768x24" bash -c 'gtk3-demo --run clipboard --autoquit'
    - xvfb-run -a -s "-screen 0 1024x768x24" bash -c 'gtk3-demo --run cursors --autoquit'

      --autoquit'

    - xvfb-run -a -s "-screen 0 1024x768x24" bash -c 'gtk3-demo --run glarea --autoquit'

    - xvfb-run -a -s "-screen 0 1024x768x24" bash -c 'gtk3-demo --run pixbufs --autoquit'
    - xvfb-run -a -s "-screen 0 1024x768x24" bash -c 'gtk3-demo --run pagesetup --autoquit'
    - xvfb-run -a -s "-screen 0 1024x768x24" bash -c 'gtk3-demo --run textscroll --autoquit'
    - xvfb-run -a -s "-screen 0 1024x768x24" bash -c 'gtk3-demo --run css_basics --autoquit'
    - xvfb-run -a -s "-screen 0 1024x768x24" bash -c 'gtk3-demo --run themeing_style_classes
      --autoquit'
    - xvfb-run -a -s "-screen 0 1024x768x24" bash -c 'gtk3-demo --run toolpalette
      --autoquit'
    - xvfb-run -a -s "-screen 0 1024x768x24" bash -c 'gtk3-demo --run event_axes --autoquit'
    - xvfb-run -a -s "-screen 0 1024x768x24" bash -c 'gtk3-demo --run list_store --autoquit'
